Package se.cbb.jprime.apps.dlrs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Delirious
    Java version of the Delirious application (previously known as GSR and GSRf) for simultaneous reconciliation and inference of a guest tree evolving inside a dated host tree.
    DLRSModel
    Implements the DLRS (a.k.a.
    DupLossProbs
    Point-wise duplication and loss probabilities for a discretised host tree.
    ParameterParser
    For more complex parameters, performs appropriate type casts, etc.
    Parameters
    Handles all regular application parameters.
    Realisation
    Represents a dated guest tree according to the DLRS model.
    RealisationSampler
    Enables sampling of realisations, i.e., dated embeddings of G in S according to the probability distribution of embeddings under the DLRS model.

    Unit tests.

    JUnit test case.
    TestDupLossProbs
    JUnit test case.
